name: The New Financial Terrorism
description: This is the first in a series of 5 NFT presentations that explore modernity, postmodern spirituality, integrity against humanity, the sin of pride, and the repression of ecosystems and bodies. There is a game involved in each NFT. There is a human pictured in this PDF, who is it? The first collector to solve the mystery gets the second NFT from the series free and will receive the clue 24 hours before it is minted.
